Annotation: Files that were telemetered during this deployment did not contain valid data with correct timestamps. Unit could have been configured to the incorrect time at deployment. In addition, the instrument stopped sending telemetered data files on 2017-04-30. Issue under investigation.

Downwelling Shortwave Irradiance (shortwave_irradiance) and Net Shortwave Irradiance (met_netsirr) minimum values jump from ~0 W m-2 to ~13-14 W m-2 and remain there through the rest of the deployment. Investigation pending.
Instrument started sending intermittent files containing bad characters, and ceased satellite transmission of files on 2017-08-02.
Instrument sending files via satellite transmission intermittently.
Instrument stopped sending files via satellite transmission.
Telemetered and recovered_host data files contain bad characters that prevent parsing data, and no data were recorded internally on the instrument.
